embedfields.name: üôä | Say
embedfields.value:
Make the bot send a Embed or Normal message
**Usage:** `!say <embed/normal> <message>`
**Required permissions:** `View Audit Log`

embedfields.name: üìä | Poll
embedfields.value:
Create a poll that can have up to 5 options.
**Usage:** `!poll`
**Required permissions:** `Administrator`

embedfields.name: üîß | Changelogs
embedfields.value:
Sends a embed message to the channel the command was send in.
**Usage:** `!changelog <version> <description>`
**Required permissions:** `Mannage Channels, Mention Everyone`
